FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our dog walking app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does the dog walking app work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app connects dog owners with trusted local dog walkers. Simply create a profile for your dog, choose available time slots, and book a walker with just a few taps.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Is the app free to use?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: The app is free to download and create a profile. We charge a small fee for each walk booking, which covers our service and insurance.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How do you ensure the safety of my dog?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: All our walkers undergo thorough background checks and training. We also provide real-time GPS tracking during walks and insurance coverage for added peace of mind.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Absolutely! Our app allows you to set up regular walking schedules daily, weekly, or custom frequencies to suit your needs.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: What if I need to cancel a walk?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: We understand plans change. You can cancel a walk up to 2 hours before the scheduled time without any charge. Late cancellations may incur a small fee.
PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Dog Walking Service
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How long are your typical dog walks?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our standard dog walks are 30 minutes long, but we offer flexible options ranging from 15-minute quick walks to 60-minute extended walks to suit your pet's needs and your schedule.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Are your dog walkers insured and background-checked?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Yes, all our dog walkers are fully insured and have undergone thorough background checks. We prioritize the safety and security of your pets and your home.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How do I book a dog walk?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Booking a dog walk is easy! Simply download our app, create an account, and schedule a walk. You can choose your preferred time, walker, and walk duration with just a few taps.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: What happens if I need to cancel a scheduled walk?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: We understand plans can change. You can cancel a scheduled walk up to 2 hours before the start time without any charge. Cancellations made within 2 hours of the walk may incur a small fee.
